StartDialogs.name: Craig When you try to get out

Dialogs.message: A job, you say? Oh, you're still working on that entrance fee, aren't you?
Dialogs.name: J2.2

Dialogs.message: Unfortunately, I don't have any gigs to offer at the moment.
Dialogs.name: J3

Dialogs.message: I'm loving that spirit! Let the games begin!
Dialogs.name: J5.1

Dialogs.message: Wait, what are you talking about? This is the game, my friend! You're in the heart of it.
Dialogs.name: J5.2

Dialogs.message: How about we dive into some games instead? This place is all about fun and games! If you win, I'll even toss you 10 BRK. Sounds like a plan?

choices.message: I am not a good gamer.

Dialogs.name: J4

Dialogs.message: Care for a quick game of heads or tails? Simply guess whether it's heads or tails, and I'll give the coin a toss. Easy enough, isn't it?
Dialogs.name: J6

Dialogs.message: Now, say your prediction.
Dialogs.name: J7

Dialogs.message: Head? OK. Let’s see!
Dialogs.name: J8.1 Head

Dialogs.message: Tail? Nice guess. OK. Let’s see!
Dialogs.name: J8.2 Tail

Dialogs.message: [ Jeremy tosses the coin into the air ]
Dialogs.name: J9.1 Head

Dialogs.message: [ Jeremy tosses the coin into the air ]
Dialogs.name: J9.2 Tail

Dialogs.message: And... The result... is....
Dialogs.name: J10.1 Head

Dialogs.message: And... The result... is....
Dialogs.name: J10.2 Tail

Dialogs.message: Head! Oh my, I'm lost.
Dialogs.name: J11.1 Head

Dialogs.message: Tail! That’s it. I’m lost.
Dialogs.name: J11.2 Tail

Dialogs.message: Ok, as promised, here are your 10 BRK.
Dialogs.name: J12

Dialogs.message: Remember to stop by when you're bored. The gaming centre is always open for you.
Dialogs.name: J13

Dialogs.message: Jobs? Nope. Not at all. The staff is currently full.
Dialogs.name: EPBS2

Dialogs.message: You are trying to pay an entrance fee right? Yeah.. 30 BRK... That’s a lot. I know.
Dialogs.name: EPBS3

Dialogs.message: Here's a little secret of mine. I was once a newcomer just like you, walking this place in search of jobs!
Dialogs.name: EPBS4

Dialogs.message: It's been a year since I joined, and now not only can I cover my entrance fee, but I'm also proudly working here as a staff member.
Dialogs.name: EPBS5

Dialogs.message: This place truly is a land of opportunity! This job has become something I love!
Dialogs.name: EPBS6

Dialogs.message: I get it. It's tough to make some BRK when you're starting from scratch and don't know where to begin.
Dialogs.name: EPBS7

Dialogs.message: Let me lend a hand! It might not be enough to cover the fee entirely, but I hope it helps.
Dialogs.name: EPBS8

Dialogs.message: And don't forget to pay it forward when you can. Small acts of kindness go a long way in making this place a better land for everyone!
Dialogs.name: EPBS9

Dialogs.message: First, you select a pool to submit the ticket to. You are free to add as many lotto tickets as you want to any pool.
Dialogs.name: SPBS2

Dialogs.message: The winners are chosen at random from the tickets added to the pool. The more ticket you add, the more chance you win!
Dialogs.name: SPBS3

Dialogs.message: There will be a draw time for each pool. The larger the prize, the longer the pool runs. We normally have daily, weekly and monthly pools.
Dialogs.name: SPBS4

Dialogs.message: This is a special moment! Currently, we have three daily NFT pools in action. They'll wrap up soon, so make sure to submit your entries to the ones that catch your eye!
Dialogs.name: SPBS5

Dialogs.message: You're still here? Congrats, you've clinched a prize!
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.1

Dialogs.message: Amazing, you submitted just one ticket and got lucky! Not everyone's that fortunate!
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.2

Dialogs.message: In the world of Web3.0, your prize has already been sent to your account. You can try equipping it in the inventory menu. Hope it suits your style!
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.3

Dialogs.message: Now, you're officially a Playbux NFT holder. This means you can dive into the Stamp to Earn feature!
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.4

Dialogs.message: Collect more Playbux NFTs by using Playbux facilities and earn extra rewards through Stamp to Earn. Don't forget to stamp daily.
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.5

Dialogs.message: For all the details about the Stamp to Earn feature, you can find everything you need to know in the Stamp to Earn building near our shop.
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.6

Dialogs.message: That's the lowdown on Playbux. I really hope you have a blast on our island and stay in touch with us.
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.7

Dialogs.message: I arrived here as a newbie too, about three months back. I spent a month working at the Playbux shop to gather enough for the entrance fee.
Dialogs.name: CILKT2

Dialogs.message: This island's pretty nice. I'm still at the Playbux shop, and you can swing by anytime.
Dialogs.name: CILKT3

Dialogs.message: I drop by every weekend. Ever heard of Lotto Pools?
Dialogs.name: CILKT4

Dialogs.message: You should check it out! Lotto Pools is a feature where you can use Lotto Tickets for a shot at some rewards.
Dialogs.name: CILKT5

Dialogs.message: My buddy just win $3,000 USDT! Talk about luck!
Dialogs.name: CILKT6

Dialogs.message: You can snag Lotto Tickets from various places in Playbux, like here, where you can use your BRK for a chance at a batch of tickets.

choices.message: I cannot spend my BRK now.

Dialogs.name: CILKT7

Dialogs.message: I know, you gotta save for that entrance fee...
Dialogs.name: CILKT8

Dialogs.message: Umm... Ever heard of Beginner's Luck?
Dialogs.name: CILKT9

Dialogs.message: It's when someone new to betting or casinos strikes gold on their very first try.
Dialogs.name: CILKT10

Dialogs.message: Why? Are you struggling financially? This isn't exactly the place for those on a tight budget.
Dialogs.name: ILKT2.1

Dialogs.message: Job? Why does everyone think they can find work here? Do you honestly believe this place needs an army of new employees?
Dialogs.name: ILKT2.2

Dialogs.message: I'm having a pretty unlucky day. How about you try your hand at the Lucky Tree for me? Maybe that Beginner's Luck thing will work for you.
Dialogs.name: CILKT11

Dialogs.message: I'll offer a little reward if you hit the jackpot.
Dialogs.name: CILKT12.1

Dialogs.message: No, you don't have to pay. I'll cover a BRK for you. No risk for you. But if you win big, I'll toss in a reward.
Dialogs.name: CILKT12.2

Dialogs.message: So... What do you say?
Dialogs.name: CILKT13

Dialogs.message: Where are you off to? No plans to swipe my BRK, right?
Dialogs.name: Craig When Player try to get out

Dialogs.message: I'm literally shaking right now! My first jackpot! Let me see those tickets, please.
Dialogs.name: C1KT2

Dialogs.message: Why? Are you trying to pull a fast one? Don't be foolish.
Dialogs.name: C1KT3.2

Dialogs.message: Oh, for real! A thousand Lotto Tickets. With this many, I'm bound to win something.
Dialogs.name: C1KT3.1

Dialogs.message: Thank you so much for this. Here's the reward I promised.
Dialogs.name: C1KT4

Dialogs.message: Oh, and please hang on to this ticket. You might want to try your luck again in the Lotto Pools.
Dialogs.name: C1KT5

Dialogs.message: Oh, bummer to hear that. But don't worry, you'll get the hang of it soon. We're gonna be globe-trotting like pros.
Dialogs.name: EPE1.2

Dialogs.message: Awesome! You're gonna love it here. We mainly zip around on it to hop between the islands.
Dialogs.name: EPE1.1

Dialogs.message: Wow, I'm totally surprised you're still sending old-school letters! These days, it's like finding a unicorn.
Dialogs.name: EPE2

Dialogs.message: Oh, by the way, I'm Edward, your friendly welcoming committee to the Mainland of Playbux!
Dialogs.name: EPE3

Dialogs.message: This island is the absolute epicenter of the Playbux universe, with thousands of folks swinging by every day. It's a land of dreams!
Dialogs.name: EPE4

Dialogs.message: Now, before we dive in, there's a little entrance fee. How about coughing up 30 BRK or 30 PBUX?
Dialogs.name: EPE5

Dialogs.message: Oh, you just got here? My bad. We're super chill with crypto payments too, like USDT or BNB!
Dialogs.name: EPE5.5

Dialogs.message: Fiat currency? Seriously, people still use that stuff? Nah, we're all about the modern ways here.
Dialogs.name: EPE6

Dialogs.message: Wait, no crypto at all? No worries, you're not the first. There are plenty of tasks around the island to earn some BRK. Just kick back and enjoy!
Dialogs.name: EPE7

Dialogs.message: There are some job around the island which can grant you some BRK. Don't worry! Take your time and have fun!
Dialogs.name: EPE8

Dialogs.message: Once you've got a total of 30 BRK in your pocket, swing by and see me at the port. I'll be waiting!
Dialogs.name: EPE9

Dialogs.message: What brings you here? Still short on that entrance fee, huh?
Dialogs.name: EP Idle

Dialogs.message: Wow, that's truly impressive! Thanks for covering the entrance fee. Now you're officially a Playbux citizen.
Dialogs.name: EPAQ2

Dialogs.message: Enjoy all the island's features! Don't forget to keep your Playbux wallet topped up for any transaction fees.
Dialogs.name: EPAQ3

Dialogs.message: You can also link your own wallet through WalletConnect or Metamask in the wallet menu.
Dialogs.name: EPAQ4

Dialogs.message: Hey there! You're the one from the letter, right? Pleasure to meet you! How was the journey?
Dialogs.name: EP1

Dialogs.message: What brings you here? Still short on that entrance fee, huh?
Dialogs.name: EPAQ1

Dialogs.message: Once again. Welcome to Playbux!
Dialogs.name: EPAQ5

Dialogs.message: Hey there! Welcome to the game center! What's your vibe today?
Dialogs.name: J1

Dialogs.message: Welcome to Shop to Earn. Where you can shop and get rewards in Playbux! How can I serve you today?
Dialogs.name: ESTE1

Dialogs.message: Welcome to the Playbux shop. How may I assist you today?
Dialogs.name: EPBS1

Dialogs.message: Hope you come to love this place, and I'm sure you'll find your opportunity. it's everywhere!
Dialogs.name: EPBS10

Dialogs.message: I will never lose again. Mark my words!
Dialogs.name: J14

Dialogs.message: Welcome to the lotto pools. Everyone has the opportunity to take part in the lottery and win rewards.
Dialogs.name: SPBS1

Dialogs.message: You've added your ticket to the [N]XXXXX pot. Well done! Just hang tight for the pools to conclude, and we'll announce the lucky winner.
Dialogs.name: SPBS6

Dialogs.message: Once again, welcome! If you need any assistance, feel free to strike up a conversation with anyone around here. We're more than happy to help!
Dialogs.name: SPBS2.8

Dialogs.message: Hi there, welcome to Lucky Tree. This is where you can exchange your BRK for a thousand Lotto Tickets. Feeling lucky, are you?

choices.message: I cannot spend my BRK now.

Dialogs.name: ILKT1

Dialogs.message: If you're in need of some BRK, I'd advise looking elsewhere. I can't take on any more staff. If I hire you, I'll have to let someone go.
Dialogs.name: ILKT3

Dialogs.message: Heard you're on the job hunt? Sorry, didn't mean to eavesdrop. Isabella's voice just carries.
Dialogs.name: CInsideLKT1

Dialogs.message: Alright, here's a BRK. Pick any tree you like and give it a shot.
Dialogs.name: CILKT14

Dialogs.message: WHATTTT! You just hit the grand prize— a thousand Lotto Tickets!! I told you, Beginner's Luck.
Dialogs.name: C1KT1

Dialogs.message: Who knows, Beginner's Luck might strike twice with this one!
Dialogs.name: C1KT6

Dialogs.message: You've landed in the right spot! Take your pick from any game you fancy. Some are on the house, while others might need a few BRK. Enjoy!
Dialogs.name: J2.1 End

Dialogs.message: So, let's make it happen!
Dialogs.name: EPE11

Dialogs.message: And hey, keep in mind, if you can't cover the entrance fee, some of the coolest Playbux features will be off-limits, and you won't get to island-hop.
Dialogs.name: EPP10

Dialogs.message: Ah! Are you the new guy looking for some BRK?
Dialogs.name: ESTE2
